These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda, almond-milk, sprite
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, lawyer, engineer, architect
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, february, july, december
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, ebony, purple, amber
 1. the mechanic is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 3. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in december is the lawyer##1
 5. the person who likes blue is somewhere to the left of the person who likes purple##5
 6. the mechanic is somewhere to the left of the person who likes ebony##5
 7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
 8. the person who likes purple is somewhere to the left of the lawyer##5
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the engineer##3
10. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere between the person who likes blue and the person drinking cola##7
11. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
12. the architect is somewhere to the right of the person who likes amber##5
13. the person who likes amber is the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Beverage   | sprite    | mirinda | almond-milk    | cola   |
| Job   | mechanic | engineer | lawyer | architect |
| Birthday           | february       | july   | december  | june     |
| Color     | blue      | purple   | amber    | ebony    |

