.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, mouse, frog, turtle
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, november, july, june
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, bike, helicopter, bus
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, fonseca, blend, alhambra
 1. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the left of the fonseca-smoker##5
 2. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bus##5
 3. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the right of the owner of the turtle##5
 4. the blend-smoker is the person driving the roller##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
 6. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the right of the owner of the frog##5
 7. the owner of the turtle is somewhere between the fonseca-smoker and the person driving the roller##7
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is in an odd position##4
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the fonseca-smoker##5
10. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the right of the cain-smoker##5
11. the person driving the bike is the alhambra-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
| Pet          | hedgehog   | frog       | turtle    | mouse      |
| Birthday   | september | june | november         | july   |
| Transport   | bus   | roller  | bike       | helicopter |
| Cigar         | cain      | blend  | alhambra | fonseca |

