 7. the person eating raspberry is not the person driving the bike##6
 8. the person driving the skateboard is not the person eating blueberry##6
 9. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
10. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
11. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
12. the person traveling to boston is the person who's hobby is gardening##1

