 7. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere between the person who growsiris and the person who growsamaryllis##7
 8. the person traveling to hannover is not the person who growsiris##6
 9. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the person who growsamaryllis##3
10. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
11. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
12. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| City         | venice      | marseilles   | hannover   | liverpool       |
| Cigar   | baccarat | siglo    | oliveros | fonseca       |
| Birthday   | february  | january | november   | september     |
| Flower         | iris   | rose    | amaryllis   | aconite |

