.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-18::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, backgammon, whist, billiard
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, begonia, poppy, sunflower
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, baseball, rowing, handball
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, car, boat, bike
 1. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 2. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the left of the person who growslily##5
 3. the person who's sport is handball is between the person driving the bike and the person driving the boat##2
 4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 5. the person who growsbegonia is not the person driving the car##6
 6. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the left of the person who growspoppy##5
 7. the person playing billiard is somewhere between the person playing scrabble and the person who growssunflower##7
 8. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5
 9. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is baseball##5
10. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
11. the person playing scrabble is the person who growspoppy##1
12. the person who growspoppy is not the person driving the boat##6

.:: Answer ::.
