The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, skateboarding, swimming, rowing
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, fuchsia, lavender, brown
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, van, roller, skateboard
 1. the person eating pomegranate is somewhere to the left of the person eating grapefruit##5
 2. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who likes emerald##2
 3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person eating watermelon##3
 4. the person eating grapefruit is on the far right##1
 5. the person who likes brown is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person driving the van is not the person who likes lavender##6
 7. the person who likes lavender is somewhere between the person who's sport is rowing and the person who's sport is surfing##7
 8. the person driving the jet-ski is not the person who's sport is surfing##6
 9. the person who likes brown is not the person who's sport is rowing##6
10. the person eating pomegranate is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
11. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
12. the person who's sport is swimming is not the person eating pomegranate##6
13. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
14. the person who likes emerald is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
