.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, rose, amaryllis, daffodil
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, kiwi, plum, tomato
City: venice, marseilles, paris, nizza
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, may, july, february
 1. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5
 2. the person eating plum is the person who growsamaryllis##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is the person traveling to nizza##1
 4. the person traveling to paris is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person who growsrose##2
 5. the person eating lettuce is somewhere to the right of the person who growsrose##5
 6. the person traveling to venice is somewhere between the person eating plum and the person who growstulip##7
 7. the person who growsdaffodil is somewhere to the left of the person eating kiwi##5
 8. the person traveling to venice is the person who's birthday is in march##1
 9. the person eating kiwi is somewhere to the left of the person eating lettuce##5
10. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far right##1
11. the person who's birthday is in july is in an even position##4
12. the person eating lettuce is somewhere to the right of the person who growsrose##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Flower   | daffodil      | amaryllis     | rose   | tulip    |
| Food     | tomato | plum   | kiwi | lettuce |
| City     | nizza        | paris     | venice  | marseilles      |
| Birthday   | may       | february | march   | july    |

 